  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要设计一个HealthTech的诊断流程图。核心是一个诊断引擎，它需要先判断是否已有患者记录。如果有，就走患者档案分支；如果没有，就进入实验室分析。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine",
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords",
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。我注意到诊断引擎既要作为起点，又要承担判断功能。您是说同一个节点既做处理又做决策分支吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，诊断引擎启动后直接进入判断逻辑。如果命中患者记录，就更新到EMR系统，然后需要循环回来重新判断——因为EMR同步后可能有新数据需要再次诊断。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine",
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords",
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先搭建主干：诊断引擎作为起始节点，然后接一个判断节点。Yes分支连到患者记录，再到EMR同步，最后回到判断节点形成循环。No分支直接到实验室分析。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine",
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords",
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync",
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "等等，判断节点的命名需要调整。为了区分，判断节点本身应该也叫HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine，因为它是同一个系统的决策状态，只是表现形式不同。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "收到，我修正一下：起始节点用矩形表示处理状态，判断节点用菱形但保持同名HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine。这样Yes/No分支从菱形引出，逻辑更清晰。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "这样设计是对的。另外EMR同步完成后必须回到判断节点，不能跳过，因为每次同步都可能触发新的诊断条件。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync",
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已调整，EMR_Sync现在有一条返回线指向判断节点。我注意到Yes分支用了常规连线，No分支到LabAnalyzer是否需要区分线型？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync",
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine",
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "No分支用虚线或者双线表示终止路径，因为实验室分析通常是最终输出，不再循环。Yes分支保持实线，表示持续迭代。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer",
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "已改为双线连接No分支。不过为了视觉区分，我实际用的是加粗长线（----），这样和Yes分支的常规线（--）对比明显。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer",
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "最后确认一下：判断节点的Yes和No标签都要明确标注，避免歧义。整个流程从诊断引擎启动，经过判断，要么循环优化患者数据，要么输出到实验室。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine",
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords",
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "完全理解。最终结构：矩形诊断引擎启动→菱形同名判断节点→Yes→患者记录→EMR同步→返回判断；No→加粗线→实验室分析。所有标签和循环关系已落实。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine",
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords",
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync",
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    }
